    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><em>此规划写于2021年国庆</em></p><h3 id="1-精通2-脚本语言"><a href="#1-精通2-脚本语言" class="headerlink" title="1. 精通2+ 脚本语言"></a>1. 精通2+ 脚本语言</h3><ul><li><code>python 2/3</code></li><li><code>Lua</code></li><li><code>TypeScript</code></li></ul><h3 id="2-精通1-Strongly-type语言"><a href="#2-精通1-Strongly-type语言" class="headerlink" title="2. 精通1+ Strongly type语言"></a>2. 精通1+ Strongly type语言</h3><ul><li><code>C++</code></li><li><code>C</code></li><li><code>C#</code></li><li><code>Java</code></li></ul><h3 id="3-实现3-大型GamePlay模块"><a href="#3-实现3-大型GamePlay模块" class="headerlink" title="3. 实现3+ 大型GamePlay模块"></a>3. 实现3+ 大型GamePlay模块</h3><ul><li>技能框架 Skill</li><li>xx战斗模块</li><li>UI模块 cocos…</li><li>FPS/TPS 射击模块</li><li>商城模块 （偏server）</li><li>时装外观模块</li><li>匹配、排行模块 （偏server+database)</li><li>…</li></ul><h3 id="4-熟悉1-phycics-engine"><a href="#4-熟悉1-phycics-engine" class="headerlink" title="4. 熟悉1+ phycics engine"></a>4. 熟悉1+ phycics engine</h3><ul><li>box2d (2d)</li><li>physx (3d)</li><li>bullet (3d)</li></ul><h3 id="5-手写一套opengl渲染框架"><a href="#5-手写一套opengl渲染框架" class="headerlink" title="5. 手写一套opengl渲染框架"></a>5. 手写一套opengl渲染框架</h3><ul><li>lighing manager</li><li>shadaw</li><li>texture</li><li>sader language</li><li>…</li></ul><h3 id="6-手写一套粗略的3d-engine"><a href="#6-手写一套粗略的3d-engine" class="headerlink" title="6. 手写一套粗略的3d engine"></a>6. 手写一套粗略的3d engine</h3><ul><li>memory malloc</li><li>object manager (scene, model…)</li><li>model (fbx)</li><li>texture and material</li><li>shader</li><li>rendering pipeline</li><li>physics (how to give better api)</li><li>animation</li><li>editor (model and scene editor?)</li><li>asset manager and tools … (like unity?)</li></ul><h3 id="7-精通Graphics"><a href="#7-精通Graphics" class="headerlink" title="7. 精通Graphics"></a>7. 精通Graphics</h3><ul><li>良好的数学基础</li><li>足够的coding实践</li><li>UE4/u3d的code learning</li></ul><h3 id="8-持续不断的English-Learning"><a href="#8-持续不断的English-Learning" class="headerlink" title="8. 持续不断的English Learning"></a>8. 持续不断的English Learning</h3><ul><li>Reading Paper (GDC…)</li><li>Reading Document (API…)</li><li>Maybe talking</li></ul><h3 id="9-Good-Coding-优秀的编程习惯"><a href="#9-Good-Coding-优秀的编程习惯" class="headerlink" title="9. Good Coding 优秀的编程习惯"></a>9. Good Coding 优秀的编程习惯</h3><ul><li>Code review</li><li>Blog record</li><li>Learn good opensource code</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
